title: The Journey of a Chicana Student at UCLA

items.title: Life of a mixed student: The Journey of a Chicana Student at UCLA
items.summary: Welcome! My name is Sofia Villalpando and I am a Mexican-American (Chicana) student who attends UCLA. For more information about me, you can visit my About Me page or my LinkedIn profile!
